          SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BirthDate], [p].[DebutId], [p].[Modified], [p].[Name], [m0].[ActorsId], [m0].[AsActorId]

      WHERE [m].[Id] = @__p_0

      SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[BirthDate], [t].[DebutId], [t].[Modified], [t].[Name], [m].[Id], [t].[AsDirectorId], [t].[DirectorsId], [t0].[AsDirectorId], [t0].[DirectorsId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Length], [t0].[Modified], [t0].[Published], [t0].[SoundTheme], [t0].[Title]
      FROM [Movies] AS [m]
      INNER JOIN (
          SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BirthDate], [p].[DebutId], [p].[Modified], [p].[Name], [m0].[AsDirectorId], [m0].[DirectorsId]
          FROM [MovieDirectors] AS [m0]
          INNER JOIN [People] AS [p] ON [m0].[DirectorsId] = [p].[Id]
      ) AS [t] ON [m].[Id] = [t].[AsDirectorId]
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT [m1].[AsDirectorId], [m1].[DirectorsId], [m2].[Id], [m2].[Length], [m2].[Modified], [m2].[Published], [m2].[SoundTheme], [m2].[Title]
          FROM [MovieDirectors] AS [m1]
          INNER JOIN [Movies] AS [m2] ON [m1].[AsDirectorId] = [m2].[Id]
          WHERE [m2].[Id] = @__p_0
      ) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DirectorsId]
      WHERE [m].[Id] = @__p_0
      ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[AsDirectorId], [t].[DirectorsId], [t].[Id], [t0].[AsDirectorId], [t0].[DirectorsId], [t0].[Id]

      FROM [Movies] AS [m]
      INNER JOIN (
          SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BirthDate], [p].[DebutId], [p].[Modified], [p].[Name], [m0].[ActorsId], [m0].[AsActorId]
          FROM [MovieActors] AS [m0]
          INNER JOIN [People] AS [p] ON [m0].[ActorsId] = [p].[Id]
      ) AS [t] ON [m].[Id] = [t].[AsActorId]
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT [m1].[ActorsId], [m1].[AsActorId], [m2].[Id], [m2].[Length], [m2].[Modified], [m2].[Published], [m2].[SoundTheme], [m2].[Title]
          FROM [MovieActors] AS [m1]

          WHERE [m2].[Id] = @__p_0
      ) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ActorsId]
      WHERE [m].[Id] = @__p_0
      ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[ActorsId], [t].[AsActorId], [t].[Id], [t0].[ActorsId], [t0].[AsActorId], [t0].[Id]

          SELECT [m0].[Id], [m0].[Length], [m0].[Modified], [m0].[Published], [m0].[SoundTheme], [m0].[Title], [m].[ActorsId], [m].[AsActorId]
          FROM [MovieActors] AS [m]
          INNER JOIN [Movies] AS [m0] ON [m].[AsActorId] = [m0].[Id]
      ) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ActorsId]
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT [m1].[ActorsId], [m1].[AsActorId], [p0].[Id], [p0].[BirthDate], [p0].[DebutId], [p0].[Modified], [p0].[Name]

      WHERE [p].[Id] = @__p_0
      ORDER BY [p].[Id], [t].[ActorsId], [t].[AsActorId], [t].[Id], [t0].[ActorsId], [t0].[AsActorId], [t0].[Id]

      SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[BirthDate], [t].[DebutId], [t].[Modified], [t].[Name], [m].[Id], [t].[ActorsId], [t].[AsActorId], [t0].[ActorsId], [t0].[AsActorId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Length], [t0].[Modified], [t0].[Published], [t0].[SoundTheme], [t0].[Title]
      FROM [Movies] AS [m]
      INNER JOIN (
          SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BirthDate], [p].[DebutId], [p].[Modified], [p].[Name], [m0].[ActorsId], [m0].[AsActorId]
          FROM [MovieActors] AS [m0]
          INNER JOIN [People] AS [p] ON [m0].[ActorsId] = [p].[Id]
      ) AS [t] ON [m].[Id] = [t].[AsActorId]
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT [m1].[ActorsId], [m1].[AsActorId], [m2].[Id], [m2].[Length], [m2].[Modified], [m2].[Published], [m2].[SoundTheme], [m2].[Title]
          FROM [MovieActors] AS [m1]
          INNER JOIN [Movies] AS [m2] ON [m1].[AsActorId] = [m2].[Id]
          WHERE [m2].[Id] = @__p_0
      ) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ActorsId]
      WHERE [m].[Id] = @__p_0
      ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[ActorsId], [t].[AsActorId], [t].[Id], [t0].[ActorsId], [t0].[AsActorId], [t0].[Id]

      INNER JOIN (
          SELECT [m0].[Id], [m0].[Length], [m0].[Modified], [m0].[Published], [m0].[SoundTheme], [m0].[Title], [m].[ActorsId], [m].[AsActorId]
          FROM [MovieActors] AS [m]
          INNER JOIN [Movies] AS [m0] ON [m].[AsActorId] = [m0].[Id]
      ) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ActorsId]
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT [m1].[ActorsId], [m1].[AsActorId], [p0].[Id], [p0].[BirthDate], [p0].[DebutId], [p0].[Modified], [p0].[Name]
          FROM [MovieActors] AS [m1]
          INNER JOIN [People] AS [p0] ON [m1].[ActorsId] = [p0].[Id]
          WHERE [p0].[Id] = @__p_0
      ) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[AsActorId]
      WHERE [p].[Id] = @__p_0
      ORDER BY [p].[Id], [t].[ActorsId], [t].[AsActorId], [t].[Id], [t0].[ActorsId], [t0].[AsActorId], [t0].[Id]

      FROM [People] AS [p]

          FROM [MovieDirectors] AS [m]

      ) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[DirectorsId]

          FROM [MovieDirectors] AS [m]

      ) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[DirectorsId]

      SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Length], [t].[Modified], [t].[Published], [t].[SoundTheme], [t].[Title], [p].[Id], [t].[ActorsId], [t].[AsActorId], [t0].[ActorsId], [t0].[AsActorId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[BirthDate], [t0].[DebutId], [t0].[Modified], [t0].[Name]
      FROM [People] AS [p]
      INNER JOIN (
          SELECT [m0].[Id], [m0].[Length], [m0].[Modified], [m0].[Published], [m0].[SoundTheme], [m0].[Title], [m].[ActorsId], [m].[AsActorId]
          FROM [MovieActors] AS [m]
          INNER JOIN [Movies] AS [m0] ON [m].[AsActorId] = [m0].[Id]
      ) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ActorsId]
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT [m1].[ActorsId], [m1].[AsActorId], [p0].[Id], [p0].[BirthDate], [p0].[DebutId], [p0].[Modified], [p0].[Name]
          FROM [MovieActors] AS [m1]
          INNER JOIN [People] AS [p0] ON [m1].[ActorsId] = [p0].[Id]
          WHERE [p0].[Id] = @__p_0
      ) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[AsActorId]
      WHERE [p].[Id] = @__p_0
      ORDER BY [p].[Id], [t].[ActorsId], [t].[AsActorId], [t].[Id], [t0].[ActorsId], [t0].[AsActorId], [t0].[Id]

          FROM [MovieActors] AS [m]

      WHERE [p].[Id] = @__p_0
      ORDER BY [p].[Id], [t].[ActorsId], [t].[AsActorId], [t].[Id], [t0].[ActorsId], [t0].[AsActorId], [t0].[Id]

          FROM [MovieActors] AS [m0]
          INNER JOIN [People] AS [p] ON [m0].[ActorsId] = [p].[Id]
      ) AS [t] ON [m].[Id] = [t].[AsActorId]
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT [m1].[ActorsId], [m1].[AsActorId], [m2].[Id], [m2].[Length], [m2].[Modified], [m2].[Published], [m2].[SoundTheme], [m2].[Title]
          FROM [MovieActors] AS [m1]
          INNER JOIN [Movies] AS [m2] ON [m1].[AsActorId] = [m2].[Id]
          WHERE [m2].[Id] = @__p_0
      ) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ActorsId]
      WHERE [m].[Id] = @__p_0
      ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[ActorsId], [t].[AsActorId], [t].[Id], [t0].[ActorsId], [t0].[AsActorId], [t0].[Id]

          SELECT [m0].[Id], [m0].[Length], [m0].[Modified], [m0].[Published], [m0].[SoundTheme], [m0].[Title], [m].[ActorsId], [m].[AsActorId]
          FROM [MovieActors] AS [m]
          INNER JOIN [Movies] AS [m0] ON [m].[AsActorId] = [m0].[Id]
      ) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ActorsId]
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT [m1].[ActorsId], [m1].[AsActorId], [p0].[Id], [p0].[BirthDate], [p0].[DebutId], [p0].[Modified], [p0].[Name]
          FROM [MovieActors] AS [m1]

          WHERE [p0].[Id] = @__p_0
      ) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[AsActorId]
      WHERE [p].[Id] = @__p_0
      ORDER BY [p].[Id], [t].[ActorsId], [t].[AsActorId], [t].[Id], [t0].[ActorsId], [t0].[AsActorId], [t0].[Id]

      FROM [Movies] AS [m]
      INNER JOIN (
          SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BirthDate], [p].[DebutId], [p].[Modified], [p].[Name], [m0].[ActorsId], [m0].[AsActorId]
          FROM [MovieActors] AS [m0]
          INNER JOIN [People] AS [p] ON [m0].[ActorsId] = [p].[Id]
      ) AS [t] ON [m].[Id] = [t].[AsActorId]
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT [m1].[ActorsId], [m1].[AsActorId], [m2].[Id], [m2].[Length], [m2].[Modified], [m2].[Published], [m2].[SoundTheme], [m2].[Title]
          FROM [MovieActors] AS [m1]
          INNER JOIN [Movies] AS [m2] ON [m1].[AsActorId] = [m2].[Id]
          WHERE [m2].[Id] = @__p_0
      ) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ActorsId]
      WHERE [m].[Id] = @__p_0
      ORDER BY [m].[Id], [t].[ActorsId], [t].[AsActorId], [t].[Id], [t0].[ActorsId], [t0].[AsActorId], [t0].[Id]

          SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BirthDate], [p].[DebutId], [p].[Modified], [p].[Name], [m0].[ActorsId], [m0].[AsActorId]
          FROM [MovieActors] AS [m0]
          INNER JOIN [People] AS [p] ON [m0].[ActorsId] = [p].[Id]
      ) AS [t] ON [m].[Id] = [t].[AsActorId]
